title: Modern Luxury Condo with City Views
description: Stunning modern condo featuring floor-to-ceiling windows with breathtaking city views. This luxurious unit boasts high-end finishes throughout, including hardwood floors, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The open-concept living space is perfect for entertaining, while the master suite offers a private retreat with an en-suite bathroom.

title: Charming Victorian House with Garden
description: Beautiful Victorian home featuring original architectural details including crown molding, hardwood floors, and bay windows. The spacious layout includes a formal dining room, updated kitchen with modern appliances, and a lovely backyard garden perfect for outdoor entertaining. Located in a quiet historic neighborhood.

title: Spacious Family Townhouse
description: Perfect family townhouse in a quiet residential area. Features an open floor plan on the main level, three bedrooms upstairs, and a finished basement for additional living space. The private backyard is ideal for children and pets. Close to schools, parks, and shopping.

title: Downtown Studio Apartment
address: 321 City Center Blvd, Downtown Core, NY 10004
description: Efficient studio apartment in the heart of downtown. Features modern amenities, large windows for natural light, and an open layout that maximizes space. Building amenities include fitness center, rooftop terrace, and 24/7 concierge. Walking distance to public transportation and entertainment.

title: Luxury Penthouse with Panoramic Views
description: Extraordinary penthouse offering panoramic city and water views from every room. This sophisticated residence features premium finishes, a gourmet kitchen with top-of-the-line appliances, and a private terrace perfect for entertaining. The master suite includes a spa-like bathroom and walk-in closet.

title: Cozy Cottage with Character
description: Charming cottage home with lots of character and charm. Features original hardwood floors, exposed beams, and a cozy fireplace. The updated kitchen opens to a sunny dining area, and the bedrooms are bright and airy. Large backyard with mature trees provides privacy and tranquility.

title: Modern Waterfront Condo
description: Stunning waterfront condo with unobstructed water views and modern amenities. Floor-to-ceiling windows showcase the beautiful harbor, while the open layout creates a seamless flow between living spaces. The building offers resort-style amenities and is walking distance to restaurants and entertainment.

title: Renovated Brownstone
address: 999 Heritage Row, Historic Brownstone District, NY 10008
description: Beautifully renovated brownstone combining historic charm with modern conveniences. Features original details like medallion ceilings and pocket doors, plus a fully updated kitchen and bathrooms. Three floors of living space include a garden level with separate entrance, perfect for rental income or home office.

title: Contemporary Loft Space
description: Spacious contemporary loft in vibrant arts district. Features soaring ceilings, exposed brick walls, and oversized windows that flood the space with natural light. The open layout is perfect for both living and working, with a modern kitchen and stylish finishes throughout. Walking distance to galleries and trendy restaurants.

title: Suburban Family Home
address: 222 Elm Street, Family Friendly Suburbs, NY 10010
description: Perfect family home in desirable suburban neighborhood. Features four bedrooms, two full bathrooms, and an eat-in kitchen that opens to the family room. The finished basement provides additional living space, and the large backyard is ideal for children and entertaining. Top-rated school district.
